.SH NAME
.PP
traceStatus \- Show the tracking status of the current program.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\f[B]\f[I]db.traceStatus()\f[]\f[]
.SH CATEGORY
.PP
Sdb
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Show the tracking status of the current program.
.SH PARAMETERS
.PP
None
.SH RETURN VALUE
.PP
