For more detial, please reference to Troubleshooting.
.SH EXAMPLES
.IP \[bu] 2
Enable trace
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
> db.traceOn( 100, new SdbTraceOption().components( "dms" ).functionNames( "_dmsStorageUnit::insertRecord" ).threadTypes( "RestListener" ) )
\f[]
.fi
.IP \[bu] 2
